    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors assessed at minimum level 1 are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for MRL 2. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the engineering decision for Class II CPB device hemolysis evaluation. Package accepted with recommendation to advance model form and equivalency assessments at next development stage.",
